[{"id":"VR857471","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows mirrors 1 and 2. Mirror 1 is oriented horizontally and joined together with Mirror 2 forming an angle labeled 130 degrees. A light ray originating from the left travels towards Mirror 1 and strikes Mirror 1 at an angle labeled 20 degrees from the surface of Mirror 1.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR857471.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two flat mirrors, Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, are joined together and meet at an angle of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"130 degrees\"><math alttext=\"130 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>130</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. A light ray is incident on Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> at an angle of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"20 degrees\"><math alttext=\"20 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>20</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span> from the mirror’s surface. The ray is reflected from Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and is then incident on Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, where it is reflected a second time. What is the angle between the final reflected ray and the surface of Mirror <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR857471_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"20 degrees\"><math alttext=\"20 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>20</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"30 degrees\"><math alttext=\"30 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>30</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"70 degrees\"><math alttext=\"70 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>70</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"80 degrees\"><math alttext=\"80 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>80</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]